title: Dolphin.GameCube.Emulator.x86-[AZkiller7]
description:
This is Dolphin, an award winning Nintendo Gamecube Emulator well known of its ease of use and performance.

--- x86 build ---

--- Minimum requirements ---

- any Dual Core cpu rated at 2Ghz
- 100% compliant OpenGL 2 Video Card with the latest drivers
- Windows Xp SP2/SP3 x86 or Windows Vista x86 ONLY

--- Note ---

Most games are playable but some still has few graphical/sound bugs.

Example of a 100% compatible game : RESIDENT EVIL ZERO.
